rs. And on this matter, many Americans are justifiably worried.\par \par \uc2 Speaking of Mr. Buffett: Now that class A shares in his \uc2 Berkshire Hathaway\uc2  conglomerate have surpassed $300,000 each -- they closed on Friday at $301,525 -- the WSJ looked at which of its products that could buy you.\par \par \uc2 If you can't buy Bitcoin ...\par \par \uc2 Then \uc2 Dogecoin\uc2  -- the parody virtual currency inspired by an animal meme -- may be your ticket to digital riches. Its market capitalization surpassed $2 billion on Saturday and was hovering just under that level this morning.\par \par \uc2 A potentially big initial coin offering: The messaging app Telegram plans to create its own virtual currency and hopes to raise as much as $500 million in a pre-sale I.C.O., according to TechCrunch.\par \par \uc2 Revolving Door\par \par \uc2 Marcelo Claure\uc2 , the C.E.O. of \uc2 Sprint\uc2 , and \uc2 Rajeev Misra\uc2 , the head of SoftBank's Vision Fund, will join Uber's board following the ride-hailing giant's share sale to a SoftBank-led group.\par \par \uc2 The Speed Read\par \par \uc2 What happened when the U.S. tried to hold a Swiss banker personally accountable for creating accounts for Americans hiding money from tax collectors. (\uc2 NYT\uc2 )\par \par \uc2 Saudi Aramco\uc2 , along with some of the kingdom's biggest companies, will raise pay after a royal order extended handouts to government workers to ease discontent over prices. (Bloomberg)\par \par \uc2 Martin Shkreli\uc2  is no longer around to deflect attention from a play by drug companies: to start prices high, then raise them incrementally. (\uc2 NYT\uc2 )\par \par \uc2 Mexico is rejecting one of the Trump administration's \uc2 Nafta\uc2  demands: a provision that could block its truckers from making deliveries into the middle of the U.S. (\uc2 NYT\uc2 )\par \par \uc2 Indians are proving reluctant to switch to digital payments, despite intensive efforts by the government and global technology companies. (\uc2 NYT\uc2 )\par \par \uc2 Sweatcoin, an app offering rewards for exercise, has raised about $1.6 million in financing and expects to close another round soon. (\uc2 NYT\uc2 )\par \par \uc2 The distribution system for legal marijuana sales in California is already showing signs of strain. (WaPo)\par \par \uc2 China's investment banks have taken some big names public in Hong Kong, but they haven't extended the strength in initial public offerings further. (Bloomberg)\par \par \uc2 SpaceX\uc2  successfully launched a \uc2 U.S. government\uc2  spacecraft called Zuma and landed its rocket back on Earth. (CNBC)\par \par \uc2 Chinese movie audiences showed little love this past weekend for ''Star Wars: The Last Jedi,'' which has collected $1.2 billion worldwide. (Deadline)\par \par \uc2 The latest to be punished in the Libor benchmark-manipulation scandal is a former Royal Bank of Scotland trader, Neil Danziger. He was fined $338,000 and banned from working in finance. (Bloomberg)\par \par \uc2 We'd love your feedback as we experiment with the writing, format and design of this briefing . Please email thoughts and suggestions to bizday@nytimes.com.\par \cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b CO\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 calsrs : \uc2 California State Teachers  Retirement System | janapl : \uc2 JANA Partners LLC | applc : \uc2 Apple Inc. | pblczn : \uc2 Public Citizen\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15